1564
01:37:21,334 --> 01:37:22,367
[grunts]

1565
01:37:22,802 --> 01:37:25,501
-[Mike grunts]
-[Shankar groans]

1566
01:37:25,970 --> 01:37:27,599
-[Mike grunts]
-[Shankar groans]

1567
01:37:30,645 --> 01:37:33,308
-[loud thuds]
-[Jeet groans]

1568
